Moyo Lawal amuru na Badagry town na Lagos state, Nigeria bu onye omere Nollywood
Ọ meriri ihe nrite "Mkpughe nke afọ" na Best of Nollywood Awards na 2012
Amụrụ Lawal na obodo Badagry wee nweta akwụkwọ praịmarị, sekọndịrị na mahadum na Naịjirịa
O nwetara akara ugo mmụta BSc na Mmeputa Nka na Mahadum Lagos
Lawal malitere ime ihe nkiri n'obere ihe nkiri mgbe o kwenyesiri ike na ọ ga-amalite ime ihe omume site na enyi ya mgbe ọ nọ n'ụlọ akwụkwọ
O sonye na ihe nkiri Next Movie Star Nigerian TV ihe igosi eziokwu  mana o nweghi ihe ịga nke ọma na ya
Lawal Na mbipụta 2012 Best of Nollywood Awards nke bu BON Awards nwetara ihe nrite maka Mkpughe nke afọ
